  "dateModified": "2025-04-01",
  "datePublished": "2025-04-01",
  "description": "The Moon is waxing through Leo today, having gathered light since the Aries New Moon on March 29. This is a building phase, emotionally and archetypally—a time of becoming visible, becoming formed. Leo doesn’t just feel, it performs its feelings. But with the Moon still early in her wax, there’s a tender edge to that performance. The desire to express is strong, but the form isn’t settled yet. You may find yourself trying on different versions of sincerity, watching which ones make others glow, and which fall flat. That’s not inauthenticity. It’s rehearsal.\n",
